snippet.title: War Wind 2: Human Onslaught Intro
snippet.description:
An old game i used to play, and one of the most underestimated ones i have known, good game play, short and sweet. there is no online multiplayer though, but you can make your own scenarios to play.

This game is available for download from here:
http://www.gamestorrents.com/pc-game-war-wind-ii-human-onslaught-english-english-descargar-torrent-7078.html

Made by the entities mentioned in the video.

Video made possible because of:

Debut Video Capture Software
http://www.nchsoftware.com/capture/in...
Rad Video Tools (Smackplay)
http://www.radgametools.com/bnkdown.htm

DreamForge Intertainment, Inc. was shut down on 10 September 2001, One of the most underestimated companies in the gaming industry.
